high_descs: Turn and go across the room past the fridge on the right and take a left after the counter on the left.
Pick up the chef's knife on the end of the counter.
Move over to the left on the same counter.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Set the knife down on the counter.
Pick a tomato slice on the counter.
Take the tomato slice to the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave.
Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Set the tomato slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Set a cooked tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go across the kitchen around the counter to the other side.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter next to the red bottle.
Turn left and go around to the counter with red tomato and red bottle on top.
Slice the red tomato on the counter top.
Place the yellow knife on the left of the white and blue magazine on the top of the counter.
Pick up one slice of the tomato from the counter top.
Turn left and go around the counter through the kitchen to the stove on the right.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave above the stove and take it out.
Move over left to the counter space on the left of the stove.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of the orange glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato on the counter.

high_descs: turn to the left and move forward all the way across the room, turn left at the window and move towards the door, turning to the left at the door to face the counter top
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the counter
move to the left a few steps to face the counter in front of the tomato
slice the tomato that is on the counter with the knife
put the knife on the counter
pick up the end slice of the tomato from the counter
turn to the left to move to the end of the counter and make a right, move forward passed the fridge on the left and turn right and move forward to the stove
open the door of the microwave that is above the stove, put the tomato slice in to the microwave,  cook the slice for 3 seconds, open the door and remove the tomato slice
move slightly to the left to face the small counter to the left of the stove
put the tomato slice on to the counter to the right of the potato
anns.task_desc: put a cooked tomato slice on to the counter
